{
  "stem": "25598.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I soon found out who lives where and who has an affair with whom and who brings flowers to whom and whatever, like the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I was sweeping, but I was watching.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it turned out to be interesting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until one day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the government built an incin-- was-- they were planning to build an incinerator in Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were selecting samples of garbage from different streets and different areas to put them through the lab to see how much energy-- agricultural, domestic, or industrial garbage, and I can tell you all the details about that-- would generate for using-- for how much energy it would generate to be used for warming-- for heating a student dorms or whatever other public facilities.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, the streets- the one street in my area which I was sweeping was chosen for that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was asked to select samples every day, and I was given this little glass tube, and I was supposed to mark on it at what time I selected it and where, and is it domestic garbage or is it leaves or what have you.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, I mean, I-- I did what I was supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had a good handwriting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I had finished high school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was well read.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had finished university.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my samples were-- looked a lot better than many of the other samples, which were taken by people who are not as literate or as educated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that got me into a whole new, very interesting and sad story, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] namely, the person who was in charge with the lab, with all the research for this incinerator, was a Jewish woman who had never been deported.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She lived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
